Practising the 3Rs in Singapore (Reduce  Reuse  Recycle) helps to achieve sustainable living by reducing waste  conserving resources and minimizing the negative impact on the environment.Reduce: By reducing consumption  less waste is generated. This helps to conserve resources and reduce demand for energy  land and water.Reuse: By reusing items  the lifespan of products is extended  reducing the need for manufacturing new products. This helps to conserve resources and reduce waste.
